C++ executable configured with Bazel
------------------------------------


1. Build the test
-----------------

> bazel build //tests:physicsLibTest


2. Build the executable
-----------------------

> bazel build //:groundstate


3. Test the project
-------------------

> bazel test //tests:physicsLibTest

4. Run the executable
---------------------

> bazel run //:groundstate


HINT:
All the above steps can be summarized by the following commands:
> bazel test ...
> bazel run groundstate
